question: What will be the US Unemployment Rate (U-3) for December 2025?
description: Predict the official U-3 Unemployment Rate released in the BLS 'Employment Situation' report for Dec 2025. Note: Release date is Jan 9 (2nd Friday) due to holidays.
resolutionCriteria:
Resolves to the seasonally adjusted U-3 rate in Table A-1 of the BLS release on Jan 9, 2026.
- Hard Lock: 8:00 AM ET (30 mins before release).
- Value: First released number (Preliminary). Revisions ignored.
